snippet.title: Dreadhalls - Gear VR Teaser
snippet.description:
First footage from the Gear VR version of Dreadhalls.
http://dreadhalls.com

Dreadhalls is a Virtual Reality horror game currently in development, inspired by the roguelike and dungeon crawler genres.
